Class Player

  • java.lang.Object
    • MovingImage
      • Player

  • public class Player
extends MovingImage
    This class represents a Player that holds a racket. This player can move left and right and swing.

      • getSwingStatus

        public int getSwingStatus()
        Determines the player's current swinging motion.
        Returns:
        -3: ready to be swung -2: rewinding from underhand -1: rewinding from overhand 0: not swinging, not ready to be swung 1: underhand swing 2: overhand swing

      • setSwingStatus
